      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SHAPIRO--Glenn N. on January 6th, 2007, of Brooklyn, NY. Beloved son of the late Sheldon and Dorothy Shapiro. Dear brother of Jay Shapiro and brother-in-law of Dr. Rick Reinkraut of Cambridge, MA, and cherished partner of Hal Levine of Brooklyn, NY. He will surely be missed and always remembered.</p>
